From 59dcfbfaa0bbb4a04e8138e08d0996c91800c486 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dropy Dev <dev@dropy.in>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 13:59:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: exit intent popup + cart reserved timer
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Admin page /app/exit with popup + timer settings
- Proxy endpoint /apps/rewards/exit/config (5min cache)
- Theme extension: exit-intent (app embed block)

Popup features:
- Desktop: mouseleave from viewport top
- Mobile: idle timer (configurable, default 20s)
- Both: visibilitychange (tab/app switch)
- 3-tier escalation (reminder → discount → urgency)
- Anti-annoyance: session limit, 72h cooldown, 7-day dismiss,
  max 3 lifetime shows, min pages, min seconds, conversion cookie
- Cart total + item count display
- Free gift reminder callout
- Discount code display per tier

Cart timer features:
- 'Items reserved for you' countdown (default 15min)
- Progress bar drain animation
- Soft expiry: shows urgency message, never clears cart
- Silent reset on user interaction
- Resets on add-to-cart
- Injects into cart page + cart drawer

All config managed from Supabase loyalty_config (key: exit_config)
Uses XHR (not fetch) per dropy.in theme requirement
